<div class="community-highlight">
  <div class="community-highlight__contributors">
    <h3 class="contributors-heading">Monthly top contributors</h3>

    {{#if this.topContributors.length}}
      <div class="contributors-list">
        {{#each this.topContributors as |item|}}
          <div class="contributor-row">
            <div class="contributor-left">
              <img src="{{avatar-url item.user.avatar_template 96}}" class="contributor-avatar">
              <div class="contributor-names">
                <div class="contributor-username">{{item.user.username}}</div>
                <div class="contributor-name">{{item.user.name}}</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="contributor-posts">
              <div class="contributor-count">{{item.post_count}}</div>
              <div class="contributor-label">Posts</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        {{/each}}
      </div>
    {{else}}
      <p class="no-contributors">No top contributors yet — start posting to appear here!</p>
    {{/if}}

    <div class="contributors-see-more">
      <a href="/u?order=post_count&period=monthly">See more +</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="community-highlight__quote">
      “The Ambassador program not only brings like-minded people together with their
      passion about making projects visible and clear, but also opens up ideas and
      user cases through global connections. Seeing the diverse usage of Asana and
      receiving regular product updates are what make the community extremely valuable.”
    <div class="quote-author">
      <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/48" class="author-avatar">
      <div class="author-info">
        <p class="author-name">Rashad Issa</p>
        <p class="author-location">United Kingdom</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

